[Nouns] punctuality, promptness, immediateness.
[Verbs] be prompt, be on time, be in time; arrive on time; be in the nick of time.
[Adjectives] timely, seasonable, in time, punctual, prompt.
[Adverbs] on time, punctually, at the deadline, precisely, exactly; right on time, to the minute; in time; in good time, in military time, in pudding time, in due time; time enough; with no time to spare, by a hair's breadth.
